<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- Title Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/imgs/favicon-32x32.png"/>
    <!-- Google fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:wght@100&family=Roboto:wght@100;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- MaterializeCSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">
    <!-- Font-awesome -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- External css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/normalize.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" type="text/css">
    <title>Bo-TOW</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
    <main class="index-main">
        <div class="d-flex firstArea">
            <section class="center-align">
                <h1>Enrich your towing <strong class="text-primary green-text">experience</strong></h1>
                <p>When you need roadside assistance, we are here to help. Call or create your account and schedule a tow today.</p>
                <a href="/signup" class="btn waves-effect waves-light green lighten-1">Get started</a>
                <div id='scale-demo' class="black scale-transition scale-out promo-d-none">
                    <p>Get <span class='big bold'>10%</span> off <span class="bold">promo code: BoTOW</span></p>
                    <button id="scale-demo-trigger" class="transparent scale-transition">X</button>     
                </div>
            </section>
            <div class="slider">
                <ul class="slides">
                  <li><img src="/imgs/One.JPG" alt="Wheel-lift-tow-truck-SUV-human" class="responsive-img" id="firstImg"></li>
                  <li><img src="/imgs/Two.JPG" alt="Human-shoveling-snow-SUV" class="responsive-img"></li>
                  <li><img src="/imgs/Three.JPG" alt="Wheel-lift-tow-truck-SUV-human-connecting-winch" class="responsive-img"></li>
                  <li><img src="/imgs/Four.JPG" alt="Human-operating-flatbed-winch-on-SUV" class="responsive-img"></li>
                  <li><img src="/imgs/Five.JPG" alt="SUV-loaded-onto-flatbed" class="responsive-img"></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section class="d-flex mission blue-grey lighten-4">
            <h1 class="center-align">What makes us different</h1>
        </section>
        <div class="row blue-grey lighten-4 d-flex secondArea">
            <div class="col s12 m4 l3">
                <div class="card large">
                    <div class="card-image">
                        <img src="/imgs/pexels-yan-krukov-8866721.jpg" alt="pexels-yan-krukov-8866721-headset-laptop">
                        <span class="card-title">Customer Service</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Any company can provide towing services. What sets us apart is our open line of communication. If we are running late, about to arrive or unload, I will personally keep you in the loop.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m4 l3">
                <div class="card large">
                    <div class="card-image">
                        <img src="/imgs/pexels-suntorn-somtong-1029243.jpg" alt="pexels-suntorn-somtong-1029243-variety-of-tools">
                        <span class="card-title">Diverse Fleet</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>We have a wide variety of service trucks, each suited to handle different situations, vehicles & loads.</p>
                        <p>From low clearance parking garages, motorcycles, boats, RVs, tractor-trailers, class B & C vehicles-- we have the tools to handle each job properly.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m4 l3">
                <div class="card large">
                    <div class="card-image">
                    <img src="/imgs/pexels-stephan-mÃ¼ller-753876.jpg" alt="">
                    <span class="card-title">Impounds</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                    <p>Is a vehicle abandoned on your property? We are specialized to handle private property impounds.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-action center-align">
                        <a href="/signup" class="btn waves-effect waves-light blue-grey lighten-4">Tell me more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex">
            <div class="container thirdArea">
                <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aTTrglc0jgw" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/js/materialize.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/9f91d488b5.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script>
        M.Sidenav.init(document.querySelector('.sidenav'))
        M.Slider.init(document.querySelector('.slider'))

    </script>
</body>
</html>